    <h1>Rescue Me Paris</h1>
    <p>Rescue Me is an online, searchable database of animals, specifically cats and dogs in Paris who need homes. We use the power of the Internet to connect adopters with shelter pets and help pets go from alone to adopted. We're working to help the good people at shelters and rescue groups find homes for their pets.</p>
