    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Increase public awareness of the availability of adoptable pets in Paris</li>
        <li>Elevate the status of pets to that of family member</li>
        <li>Responsible adoption</li>
    </ol>
    <picture><img src="./images/about-2.jpeg" alt=""></picture>
